msgid "Package contributions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:6
#: 9b53b744bdcb4e2e9f7d85cdbec23ce9
msgid ""
"*This page is for developers who wish to contribute packages. If you want"
" to install contributed packages, please see* :doc:`installing "
"contributed packages </user/advanced-topics/installing-contributed-"
"packages>` *.*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:8
#: 411aae844aa54504a47962ee1b02c6fc
msgid ""
"We’re very grateful to the talented and hard-working community members "
"who contribute software packages to Qubes OS. This page explains the "
"inclusion criteria and procedures for such packages, as well as the roles"
" and responsibilities of those involved."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:11
#: dc4f4c08e0364bde8b17b85369e8cb8a
msgid "Inclusion Criteria"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:14
#: 52929f935f404e4d81bff582056ac05b
msgid "In order to be accepted, packages must:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:16
#: 0f174c9894e74fb8bb07cd3df9341518
msgid "In no way weaken the security of Qubes OS."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:18
#: ea3ac9462e224dd2aa7dd7e89f64e4c1
msgid ""
"Be published under an open-source license (read about the :doc:`Qubes OS "
"License </developer/code/license>`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:20
#: 54b17938420449d1809e536d519f6bc3
msgid "Follow our :doc:`coding guidelines </developer/code/coding-style>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:22
#: a626341c05ce4d8d9a12bce6a524cc4c
msgid "Be thoroughly tested."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:24
#: 75c197a561464925bd2f6ed1f791b426
msgid "Have a clearly-defined use case for Qubes users."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/package-contributions.rst:26
